column10:
Great game that so many of grew up on. Memorable story & characters (Charon, my bro)
: think twice before buying on Windows though, I can't seem run it no matter how many fixes I apply to it. If you can manage to run it on PC, please note that it's very easy for your save files to get corrupted, I hear CASM (Nexus mods fix) helps with that.

@Bethesda, please fix this game....and also remaster too pls? thx
